\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12001033 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6567477\charrsid11805643 '84.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6105384 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6567477\charrsid11805643 And where were you born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12001033 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6567477\charrsid11805643 In Liverpool but I couldn't say where. Possibly where I was born had been demolished.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6105384 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6567477\charrsid11805643 Would you know how long you lived in the house you were born in? Which is the house you can remember most as a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12001033 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6567477\charrsid11805643 In Berkely Street, in - that's off Mossley by St Cleavers Church.
