\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6105384 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6567477\charrsid11805643 It wasn't a regular thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12001033 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6567477\charrsid11805643 No. No.
