\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12001033 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6567477\charrsid11805643 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6105384 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6567477\charrsid11805643 Did she make her own jam or bottle fruit or vegetables?
