Well I don't think they were very keen on anything out of a tin really. It might have been - an occasional tin of salmon but nothing else I don't think, no. Of course there wasn't a lot of tinned - those days, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6105384 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6567477\charrsid11805643 Did they keep any livestock for the family - any hens pigs or goats?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12001033 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6567477\charrsid11805643 Oh no. Sometimes we had a cat. But that's about all.
