\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12001033 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6567477\charrsid11805643 Oh sometimes, it just depended.
