\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6105384 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6567477\charrsid11805643 What was your parents attitude if you left some food uneaten on your plate?
